---
const pillars = [
  {
    n: '01',
    title: 'Technical Leadership\n& Architecture',
    sub: 'Systems that survive\ncontact with reality.',
  },
  {
    n: '02',
    title: 'Product\nOwnership',
    sub: 'Technology without\nproduct judgment is\nexpensive noise.',
  },
  {
    n: '03',
    title: 'AI Strategy\n& Integration',
    sub: 'Knowing what AI should replace, what it should augment, and what must stay human.',
  },
];
---

<section id="what-i-do" class="wid-section">

  <div class="wid-layout">

    <!-- Left: hero intro -->
    <div class="wid-intro">
      <div class="wid-header">
        <span class="section-label">— What I Do</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-eyebrow fade-in" data-delay="100">
        <span>CTO</span>
        <span>Product</span>
        <span>AI</span>
        <span>Creative Technology</span>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-body fade-up" data-delay="200">
        Twenty years building technology in places where it really had to work —
        AI platforms, real-time systems, live performances in front of thousands.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: pillars -->
    <div class="wid-right">
      <div class="wid-lead fade-up" data-delay="0">
        <p>
          The hardest problems are never purely technical — they live between what's possible,
          what's right for the user, and what the team can actually sustain.
          <strong>Twenty years across engineering, product, and creative direction</strong>
          has given me a useful perspective on
          <strong>where things tend to go wrong.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="wid-grid">
        {pillars.map((p, i) => (
          <div class="pillar fade-up" data-delay={String(i * 90)}>
            <span class="pillar-num">{p.n}</span>
            <h3 class="pillar-title">{p.title}</h3>
            <p class="pillar-sub">{p.sub}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .wid-section {
    background: #F0EDE6;
    padding: 6rem 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #D4CFC6;
  }

  /* Two-column layout */
  .wid-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Left column */
  .wid-intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .wid-header {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #9A9288;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow span {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #D4CFC6;
    background: #0E0D0B;
    padding: 0.3em 0.65em;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #6B6456;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  /* Right column */
  .wid-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .wid-lead {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .wid-lead p {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #6B6456;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .wid-lead strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #0E0D0B;
  }

  /* ── Grid: brutalist horizontal rule dividers ── */
  .wid-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    border-top: 2px solid #0E0D0B;
  }

  .pillar {
    padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2.5rem 0;
    border-right: 1px solid #D4CFC6;
  }
  .pillar:last-child { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; }
  .pillar:not(:first-child) { padding-left: 2.5rem; }

  .pillar-num {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #C4BFB6;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }

  .pillar-title {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.2vw, 1.75rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: #0E0D0B;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    white-space: pre-line;
  }

  .pillar-sub {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #9A9288;
    white-space: pre-line;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .wid-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .wid-intro { position: static; }
    .hero-eyebrow { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .wid-section { padding: 4rem 1.75rem; }
    .wid-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      border-top: 2px solid #0E0D0B;
    }
    .pillar {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #D4CFC6;
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
    .pillar:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .pillar:not(:first-child) { padding-left: 0; }
  }
</style>
